name: Expanse AWD International Carry-On Wheeled Luggage

features: The interior compression straps keep your clothing and other items snug, minimizing wrinkles and maximizing packing space
Our No Matter What™ Warranty assures that you are spending your money wisely, knowing your bag will be repaired or replaced no matter what trouble comes your way
A vertical quick stash pocket helps keep important items within reach, its unique orientation makes it easy to get in and out of your bag even when it’s in the overhead compartment
Ultra-durable, multi-directional wheels stored in a heavy-duty wheel housing keep you rolling along anywhere your life takes you
Innovative Bi-Tech™ Armor Lite technology helps make this pack abrasion resistant in high wear areas which allows you to focus on your travels knowing your gear is solid
Fabric blocking technology helps hide the scuffs and stains of travel keeping your bag looking new for years to come
Grab handles on the top, side and bottom make it ideal to get moving in an instant
Mesh ID pocket to stash your ID, contact info or business cards
The padded tablet sleeve is ideal to keep your device protected, while always within reach so you can stay connected to your digital life
Whether you’re in an urban jungle or rural countryside, the Central Lock Point with Secure Zip™ Toggles protects your valuables from others getting into your bag
Use a carabiner or clip to latch purses, water bottles, and more to the bag’s external lash points, ideal for gear you don’t feel like carrying anymore
